1
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] Dobrodošli u dvadeset i peti mali jubilejan čušpjez i normalno malo je specijalan.

2
00:00:32,719 --> 00:00:35,679
[SPEAKER_00] Danas opet imamo dva gosta za Viktora.

3
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:39,439
[SPEAKER_00] je meni lako, ali danas je s nama i Harisov Jastreb, imenovan.

4
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] James.

5
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] A Bond.

6
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,240
[SPEAKER_01] Bond, James.

7
00:00:42,719 --> 00:00:43,200
[SPEAKER_01] Double Ew.

8
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, evo.

9
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] Viktor Šegar, Sokolar.

10
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:49,439
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, Viktor Šegar, Sokolar Karlović.

11
00:00:49,679 --> 00:00:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] Karlović.

12
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:50,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

13
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,159
