00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

621
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj, ako imaš ti pravo na mišljenje, što ja nemam pravo na mišljenje.

622
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,480
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, je li to sloboda i demokracija?

623
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja se s tim ne slažem.

624
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ti si onda.

625
00:40:16,559 --> 00:40:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, odmah si.

626
00:40:17,679 --> 00:40:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Krkanec.

627
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, odmah si ekstremni desničar.

628
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to mi je.

629
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto sam uvijek rekao patriotizam, uvijek, nacionalizam.

630
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] To mi ne pada na pamet.

631
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] Patriotizam, uvijek prije svega.

632
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] Voliti svoje, isto tako poštivati svoje ljude.

633
00:40:29,039 --> 00:40:29,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, to je tuđe.

634
00:40:29,679 --> 00:40:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš kako je?

635
00:40:30,159 --> 00:40:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja dođem, imam prijatelja u Englesku, ako oni u šest sati piju čaj.

636
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:37,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne mogu ja reći da oni svi moraju piti kavu u tri po pola ručka.

637
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:38,639
[SPEAKER_01] U kojoj si ok, ekipa, po to je vaše.

638
00:40:39,199 --> 00:40:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] Samo dođeš i poštuješ.

639
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

640
00:40:40,639 --> 00:40:41,280
