654
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ono.

655
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kužim, pa moja.

656
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je počela smetati ta isključivost.

657
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Moja dvorište, moja pravila.

658
00:41:35,679 --> 00:41:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, da.

659
00:41:36,559 --> 00:41:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ti dođeš poštoš moje, dođemo tvoje.

660
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ne silim te da rešče valove.

661
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:43,599
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, mi smo jedino ovdje prekršili pravila Jamesa.

662
00:41:44,239 --> 00:41:44,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da man nije.

663
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:45,760
